title: Midnight in the Desert with Art Bell - 2015-11-05.mp3
description:
Hi all, 

This is my copy of the November 5th broadcast of Midnight in the Desert with Art Bell. It's the full show, all three hours. 

I captured it via a Linux program, and converted it to MP3 at 64 Kbps. I'm really new at this, so I'm only trying to fill the missing show. I just wanted to make it available, because I rely on others to post it and since this one wasn't there, I decided to upload it myself. I have the original AAC file if anyone asks for it, but that's up to you guys. 

So please let me know if this helps for the show. 

Thanks
